{"tid":1200861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[人噴我又噴] 比噴髮膠噴到隻眼好辛苦","createTime":"2019-06-11T00:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T06:38:57.000Z","uid":15488,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"dca512e48b7e55f2ee3a8fcae0585195f10f79e8","tid":1200861,"uid":15488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:26:02.000Z","msg":"最近學人gel 頭噴野<br />\n點知今朝一個唔小心嚇到自己隻眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n眼鏡都矇哂 要除黎洗 <br />\n唔係就野都睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該無永久性傷害 不過中左招之後搞左好耐先無事<br />\n影響哂今日既返工安排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://338.dyndns.biz/archived/2012//uploads/34408_12770194.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F338.dyndns.biz%2Farchived%2F2012%2F%2Fuploads%2F34408_12770194.jpg&h=1ec62e98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家認住佢 各大藥房超市都有得買 小心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家用既時候一定要小心<br />\n更加唔好幫其他人噴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1281d54416f5a18527eeeed3b4e1494d38c79155","tid":1200861,"uid":15488,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:27:21.000Z","msg":"好彩無色 有色既話眼鏡都唔洗要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc036df4d923af51ef90aa6bbd35a2645c43156","tid":1200861,"uid":15488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa41d7a9b4f49a274f59c4f1d72cac7553d50107","tid":1200861,"uid":15488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:31:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gi